{"tid":2324571,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣拒絕約出去食飯？","createTime":"2020-12-14T04:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T00:34:16.000Z","uid":144559,"like":11,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"95fca1559f7431832e7259b1d2dc0389a13f1085","tid":2324571,"uid":144559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:48:02.000Z","msg":"一年前喺app識咗個男仔<br />\n嗰陣時無聊先玩<br />\n幾岩傾咪約出嚟<br />\n點知真人好矮又多暗瘡又唔剃鬚<br />\n之後佢就話同我交換ig<br />\n咁我咪當識個朋友囉<br />\n<br />\n之後就冇再傾計<br />\n但奇奇怪怪就每隔幾個月就話約出嚟食飯<br />\n我唔係唔得閒<br />\n但我就係冇興趣同佢食<br />\n你話朋友食飯但我同佢又冇交集<br />\n唔知食嚟做咩<br />\n有時間都同啲中學同學食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係話好忙就推左<br />\n<br />\n又隔多幾個月依家又無端端約我聖誕節嗰段時間食飯<br />\n唔知點婉轉啲拒絕<br />\n唔通直接話唔好再約我咁咩"},{"pid":"6b91454d9c222e01a13e448ab56897bc7e1c5cbe","tid":2324571,"uid":2419,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"block啦 冇交集驚閪"},{"pid":"ba83d7fe6c45a81dd3c18cec54e374f63d696065","tid":2324571,"uid":156549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:49:10.000Z","msg":"直接d <br />\n話有男朋友<br />\n反正唔會再見"},{"pid":"35e3c63b5f798ef4b0a276ba4a17626ccdadd7bb","tid":2324571,"uid":198401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b91454d9c222e01a13e448ab56897bc7e1c5cbe","tid":2324571,"uid":2419,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:48:50.000Z","msg":"block啦 冇交集驚閪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:49:49.000Z","msg":"true"},{"pid":"d263fb089eb859e329b0ea02ad5810e89dc99206","tid":2324571,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"唔得閒呀bye"},{"pid":"941f25e05da04500dada050414eea65542716980","tid":2324571,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba83d7fe6c45a81dd3c18cec54e374f63d696065","tid":2324571,"uid":156549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T04:49:10.000Z","msg":"直接d <br />\n話有男朋友<br />\n反正唔會再見"},"ci